attributes.mlflow.spanInputs:
{"database_schema": ""Description for table: Account"
type Account @entity @regularPolling {
  "Unique identifier for the account, represented as a byte array."
  id: Bytes!
  "List of pools associated with the account."
  pools: [Pool!]!
  "Balances of the account in each pool, represented as an array of big integers."
  poolBalances: [BigInt!]!
  "USD equivalent of the account's pool balances, represented as an array of big decimals."
  poolBalancesUSD: [BigDecimal!]!
  "List of deposits made by the account."
  deposits: [Deposit!]!
  "List of withdrawals that are queued for the account."
  withdrawsQueued: [Withdraw!]!
  "List of withdrawals that have been completed for the account."
  withdrawsCompleted: [Withdraw!]!
  "Flags indicating whether the account has withdrawn from each pool, represented as an array of booleans."
  _hasWithdrawnFromPool: [Boolean!]!
}"}
